  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Covid-19 Emergency in Italy.  We need you!</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In Italy there are 82.000 cases of Coronavirus. Emilia-Romagna, is the second-most hit region in Italy, with almost 12.000 positive cases, of which 5.000 are home-cared. Due to the spread of the virus a lot of people are isolated at home. We need you! Thanks to you we could grant healthcare staff where it is needed, volunteers for isolated people and self-protection devices for both medical personnel and volunteers.</narrative>
  </description>
